  "detailed_description": "<h1>加入我们吧！</h1><p>《筮灵》现已发售！快来官方交流群与怪谈同好们一起讨论游戏吧！<br>官方粉丝交流群：<strong>127843809</strong><br>风域游戏微博请关注<strong>@风域游戏 </strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/363151190308ee97293f37233b6d42fb.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/a604f71c6e230e4ddb490c2e4f084873.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=170 /></span><br>2018年，失踪已久的幽灵社前社长「刘洋」突然发来一条诡异的Q聊信息，将社员「展天尘」和青梅竹马「沈晓薇」引到了一个光怪离奇的规则世界之中。在调查真相的途中，便随着神秘学姐「句萤子」一同出现的，却是日常的彻底扭曲与瓦解......<br><br>玩家将以一名高中生的视角，游走于日常和诡异之间，逐渐寻找被隐藏修改的真相。当平日里无比熟悉的场景都成了被“祂们”所掌控的扭曲时空，或许唯有遵守“祂们”所定下的规则，才有机会找到一线生机。<br><br><br><strong>无限循环的六层楼梯</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/890fa5e2321d36b3c6167e1eefde6de9.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=333 /></span><br><br><strong>诡异的工厂员工细则</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/453a3c3b633a00210d78f4dbbb4c138c.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=333 /></span><br><br><strong>永远坐不满的深夜公交</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/914fdd32ffa6fc08070c62a73f05814a.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=333 /></span><br><br><strong>没有演员的光明大剧院</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/1540e61e223d333fd50e561d025c8161.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=333 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/87cc63ffccfe0cb2d295adfc873517f9.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=170 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/6689f06d6f2e1689dd1401df2064f0ae.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=259 /></span><br>江城铁路中学高二年级学生、“幽魂社”现任社团团长、“G岛论坛”现任版主。自幼拥有一种特殊的能力，能看见常人看不见的不祥事物。学长刘洋失踪之后的某天，展天尘收到了来自刘洋的信息，约定在刘洋失踪的地点“幸福里小区”中见面。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/386e1beee526ae783e4b85658dfd6565.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=259 /></span><br>在展天尘上小学时搬来他家隔壁的女生,展天尘的青梅竹马。高中时和展天尘一起加入了“幽魂社”，偶尔会和展天尘一起参与户外实地考察活动。在展天尘获得了失踪学长刘洋的行踪之后，她决定和展天尘一起前往“幸福里小区”。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/2aae107dbec657c244fc78803b29684d.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=259 /></span><br>展天尘所在班级的班长，成绩优异，对网络流行事物不甚敏感。在“幸福里事件”之后主动找上展天尘,希望让他帮自己一个很重要的忙。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/689d5fe1d8a77c243927d3a8b9fb0a04.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=259 /></span><br>展天尘的死党，家境优渥，头脑简单。不相信所谓灵异事件的存在，只对吃喝玩乐感兴趣，在调动氛围上很有一手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/c70859dba5fac2dcbb99adb5bffd2f93.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=259 /></span><br>来自一个特殊神秘家族的奇怪少女，其家族成员似乎都肩负着一种危险却重大的使命。在“幸福里事件”后，句萤子与同样调查此事的展天尘一行人邂逅。为了自己的目的，句萤子决定加入展天尘的队伍，与他们一同行动。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/9893ca52afb9d0deb8d09451ebbca7c4.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=170 /></span><br>在音效配音方面我们希望在所有玩家心中留下深刻的印象<br>本作配乐、音效都经过专门设计制作，力求最好<br>全程<strong>武汉话方言</strong>配音，邀请闲踏梧桐、大衍若空等等优秀且符合角色的配音演员合作。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201810/extras/5bb31543fd89b9248cab79a7e8a1c985.avif?t=1749635722\" width=600 height=170 /></span><br>制作组：风域游戏《筮灵》制作组<br>制作人：无痕疾风<br>主策划/演出：大型螺丝怪物<br>编剧：无痕疾风、骆涛<br>主美：六六<br>角色美术：青叶动画、不能吃的土豆、铃原奈奈<br>场景美术：大型螺丝怪物、青叶动画<br>CG美术：青叶动画、铃原奈奈<br>程序：黄涛涛<br>UI：鱼头蓝豆腐、大型螺丝怪物<br>音乐：九鸢<br>音效：大型螺丝怪物、远山<br>配音演员：大衍若空、闲踏梧桐、吱毛、桂圆翊宝、极光、鸣鸣 、史兰等",
